usbnotificationagent(8) System Manager's Manual usbnotificationagent(8)

NAME

usbnotificationagent — Agent to detect accessory issues and present a notification to the active user

DESCRIPTION

Use launchctl(1) to control usbnotificationagent

PREFERENCES

To reset suppressed notifications use defaults(1) to modify the com.apple.usbnotificationagent domain.

FILES

/System/Library/LaunchAgents/com.apple.usbnotificationagent.plist
 
/System/Library/Sandbox/Profiles/com.apple.usbnotificationagent.sb
 

SEE ALSO

launchd(1) launchctl(1) defaults(1)
